div.p:
Quest. 5. What is meant by [
                        〈 in non-Latin alphabet 〉
                     ] Gods ordaining them? Is it an Ordaining by Decree, by Law, or by Providential disposal of Event? Answ. The internal eternal Decrees of God are no Rule of Duty to us, nor the thing here meant: But his Institution of the office by the Ʋniversal Law, together with those Providential disposals that make over the Power to the individual persons.
